    • Constructor Detail

      • CachedLDAPAuthorizationMapNamespaceChangeListener

        public CachedLDAPAuthorizationMapNamespaceChangeListener​(SimpleCachedLDAPAuthorizationMap.DestinationType destinationType,
                                                         SimpleCachedLDAPAuthorizationMap.PermissionType permissionType)
        Creates a new listener. If permissionType is null, add and remove events are ignored as they do not directly affect policy state. This configuration is used when listening for changes on entries that represent destination patterns and not for entries that represent permissions.
        Parameters:
        destinationType - the type of the destination being listened for
        permissionType - the optional permission type being listened for
